'''鹰嘴豆泥'''或'''鹰嘴豆沙'''（{{lang-ar|حمص بطحينة}}、拉丁化：Hummus）是[[黎凡特|黎凡特]]食物。鹰嘴豆泥常与蔬菜、面包和烤肉一同供应。<ref>[http://www.lifeweek.com.cn/2011/1208/36017.shtml 健康食谱——鹰嘴豆泥（ Hummus）] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6QJmPgQIR?url=http://www.lifeweek.com.cn/2011/1208/36017.shtml |date=20140614060931 |dateformat=iso }}（），[[三联生活|三联生活]].</ref>

鹰嘴豆泥可以加入柠檬、大蒜、[[芝麻酱|芝麻酱]]和[[辣椒|辣椒]]。<ref>Fayed, Saad. "[http://mideastfood.about.com/od/middleeasternfood101/a/hummus101.htm Hummus Recipes] {{Wayback|url=http://mideastfood.about.com/od/middleeasternfood101/a/hummus101.htm |date=20140704020903 }}." [[About.com|About.com]].</ref>
